snippet.title: Flywrench Trailer
snippet.description:
flywrench.com
Flywrench is a game about piloting an abstract morphing bird-spaceship through a complex web of colored lines accompanied by an electronic music soundtrack curated by the world famous, Daedelus. (Song in trailer by Kuh Lida)
